comment_data.body:
how is anyone going to know the purpose of this in the future? git spelunking which leads to... a gigantic github discussion... is costly. We can easily compress the conclusion into a minimal comment.

```suggestion
      // terminal_enter unconditionally sets `mapped_ctrl_c` to avoid `got_int`. 8eeda7169aa4
      // But `got_int` may be set elsewhere, e.g. by interrupt(). So ensure that it is cleared.
      got_int = false;
```

